      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "`~bitcoin` refers to the home directory of the bitcoin user, so I think the documentation is correct as is, and this change just makes it more ambiguous. But if people are less familiar with multi-user systems than they used to be and `~bitcoin` is confusing, maybe this change is an improvement. I just don't think it's a \"fix\"",
